{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_51_03",
  "title": "kana",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影終了後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は本当に楽しかったです！\nまた機会があれば、よろしくお願いしま～す",
      "startTime": 4.4252659733,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3441.4006933999995,
          "startTime": 7.8666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4575.7746443999995,
          "startTime": 9.0010406177
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 10.0666662694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "は～、終わった終わった\nやっとストレスから解放された～",
      "startTime": 12.4558132576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "片付けは、ホテルの方々がやってくれるらしいわ\nスタッフさん達も行ったし、私達も撤収しましょう",
      "startTime": 19.4333331903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "おい、何帰ろうとしてんだよ",
      "startTime": 23.1333331903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 23.1333331903
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 26.2666665237
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "何？　もしかして、まだケーキ食べたいの？\n余ってる分、一人で食べてっていいわよ",
      "startTime": 29.9543910889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 33.2333338261
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "誰が食いしん坊だっ！　プレゼントのことに決まって\nんじゃん！　この！　ハンドクリームの！　こと！",
      "startTime": 36.3685141168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 39.8666671594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "ふざっけんな！　なんだよこれ！　なんで二人と\nお揃いな訳！？　キモ！　絶対使わねーわ！",
      "startTime": 43.0333338261,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 46.7333338261
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの撮影ではあんなに喜んでいたじゃない\nそれに、kanaも『メンバーが大好き』なんでしょう",
      "startTime": 50.2000004928,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "大好きなメンバーでお揃い。趣旨に合ってるわよね\nいい記事になるんじゃない？　私は読みたくないけど",
      "startTime": 58.266667223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 61.9999969324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "百歩譲っていい記事になったとしても、せめてリップ\nにしろよ！　同じブランドの、ほしかったんだけど",
      "startTime": 65.5333302658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "でもあれ、私の肌に合わなかったし",
      "startTime": 69.5666635991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 69.5666635991
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 72.4666595301
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "なんで自分の基準で選んでんだよ！　てか知ってたなら\n素直に買って来いよ。どんだけヘソがひん曲がってんだ",
      "startTime": 76.8944144091,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 81.8333261968
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "あー、ムカつく……\nあれ、袋の底に何か入ってる。何、この紙",
      "startTime": 84.8138655187,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 186.12583470000743,
          "startTime": 84.9999913534
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 91.5999928635
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 91.5999928635
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "『領収書。お品代、三点お買い上げ\n星見プロダクション様』……",
      "startTime": 96.0999928635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 98.3666595301
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、それ私のだから！\n読まないでよ！",
      "startTime": 100.0333262762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 101.5666585129
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "読むなも何も、これハンドクリームの領収書じゃん\nkanaへのプレゼント、経費で落としてんじゃん",
      "startTime": 105.3999918462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "てか、ちゃっかり自分達の分も落としてんじゃん！",
      "startTime": 108.6666585129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 108.6666585129
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 112.5333251795
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "別にやましいことはないわ。企画を盛り上げるためだし\nオフを返上したことを話したら、許可ももらえたもの",
      "startTime": 116.8999918462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 120.6333251795
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "どうせ丸め込んだんでしょ\n今日ばかりは、ポンコツマネージャーに同情するわ",
      "startTime": 122.9999918462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 126.6333251795
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "それとfran、立て替えたのは私よね\n本来なら私の領収書だから、返してもらえるかしら",
      "startTime": 130.5804734793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 134.3999918462
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "うわ、山田さん、理由つけて私物買った上に\n領収書をネコババする気だった訳？",
      "startTime": 138.3999918462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 141.7999918462
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違うわよ！　後でmihoに渡そうと思ってたの！\nあと山田って呼ぶな！",
      "startTime": 145.0999912104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 146.8999847254
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "本当かなぁ。山田さんってがめついし\n自販機見るたびに小銭あさってそうな顔してんじゃん",
      "startTime": 150.4333180588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 154.6333180588
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "どんな顔よ！　あと、山田って呼ぶなってば！\n次呼んだら、本当に顔にケーキぶつけるわよ！？",
      "startTime": 158.5666580201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 162.0666544439
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "逆ギレしないでもらえますー？\n山田・ネコババツィスカ・夏織さん。きゃはっ、ゴロ悪",
      "startTime": 164.9280220119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 170.5333211106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "てかぶつけられるもんならぶつけてみなよ\nただ、服が汚れたらクリーニング代払って下さいねー？",
      "startTime": 174.4336887786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_03-kan016.m4a",
